				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html">
					<font size="8"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2. I CERTIFY on my official oath that I have this day of " + new java.text.SimpleDateFormat("MMMM dd, yyyy").format(new java.util.Date()) + " paid in cash to each man whose name appears on the above roll, the amount set opposite his name, he having presented himself, established his identity, and affixed his signature or thumb mark on the space provided. Therefore unpaid services are indicating red ink through the column &quot;Amount Paid&quot;. Special Disbursing Officer, Paymaster or Municipal Treasurer ______________."]]></textFieldExpression>
